msgid "外设"
msgstr "Peripherals"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:17 101d7506d69544f8aca2a966f4c55ac9
msgid "SDIO 最⾼速度能⽀持到多少？"
msgstr "What is the maximum speed supported by SDIO?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:19 ac0aaa5e7972498282414847d6eafe44
msgid "SDIO 时钟能到 50 MHz, 理论最⾼速度是 200 Mbps。"
msgstr "The SDIO clock can reach 50 MHz, and the theoretical maximum speed is 200 Mbps."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:24 306730db47144acea9f5deb5a3fb53b5
msgid "使⽤ ESP32 做触摸相关应⽤时，哪⾥有相关资料可参考？"
msgstr "Where can I find reference materials for touch-related applications using ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:26 605158ecd6eb4b2381f39fef7153d2cf
msgid "请参考推荐的 `软硬件设计 <https://github.com/espressif/esp-iot-solution/tree/master/examples/touch_pad_evb>`_。"
msgstr "Please refer to the recommended `software and hardware design <https://github.com/espressif/esp-iot-solution/tree/master/examples/touch_pad_evb>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:31 7bb6abf7a48d4afba10aca8372a1701d
msgid "ESP-WROOM-02D 模块是否可以外接 SPI Flash ？"
msgstr "Can the ESP-WROOM-02D module connect to an external SPI Flash?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:33 b901bf3ff035444f84d0540c03e63420
msgid "ESP-WROOM-02D 有空闲 SPI 外设，可外接 SPI Flash，用以存储数据。"
msgstr "ESP-WROOM-02D has a free SPI peripheral and can connect to an external SPI Flash for data storage."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:38 e072bebdf3d74c799394961c11c71e6c
msgid "ESP-WROOM-S2 作为从机，STM32 作为 MCU ，可以使⽤ SPI 接⼝下载吗？"
msgstr "Can ESP-WROOM-S2 be used as a slave and STM32 as the MCU to download firmware through the SPI interface?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:40 463c0aa96653406d9e9180f39322ef6f
msgid "不可以，默认下载功能仅支持串口 UART0，固件启动后可应用中使能其他外设，在应用中⾃⾏设计⽀持 OTA 功能。"
msgstr "No. The default download function only supports the UART0 serial port. After the firmware starts, other peripherals can be enabled in the application, and OTA support can be designed by the user in the application."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:45 33bc500124d44cd7bd7a19c15659ef7f
msgid "ESP8266 的 SDIO 是否⽀持 SD 卡？"
msgstr "Does ESP8266 SDIO support SD cards?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:47 dfdb885786d742219020098b88a82d92
msgid "ESP8266 是 SDIO Slave，不⽀持 SD 卡。"
msgstr "ESP8266 is an SDIO Slave and does not support SD cards."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:52 69e91db2a2874c04babec8bc2b051311
msgid "ESP8266 是否支持 I2C slave 模式？"
msgstr "Does ESP8266 support I2C slave mode?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:54 313e417f2e684895b75db8572a0008ef
msgid "不支持，如果要使用此功能，推荐使用 ESP32-S2 或者 ESP32 芯片。ESP32 参考示例：`i2C_self_test <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/peripherals/i2c/i2c_self_test>`_。"
msgstr "No. If this function is required, it is recommended to use the ESP32-S2 or ESP32 chip. ESP32 reference example: `i2C_self_test <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/peripherals/i2c/i2c_self_test>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:59 892fe56bbc33408996c6b03af39bc97e
msgid "ESP32 管脚配置需要注意什么？"
msgstr "What should be noted when configuring ESP32 pins?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:61 646dd110ca8941d7b5914ce8f1a5417e
msgid "ESP32 系列模组分为 ESP32-WROOM 系列和 ESP32-Wrover 系列，GPIO 使用配置注意事项如下。"
msgstr "ESP32 series modules are divided into the ESP32-WROOM series and ESP32-WROVER series. Notes for GPIO usage and configuration are as follows."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:63 cf2a1e487096445abc62cea4822f497d
msgid "WROOM-32/32D/32U 系列共有 26 个 pin 脚可供客户使用, 注意事项如下："
msgstr "The WROOM-32/32D/32U series provides 26 pins for customer use. Notes:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:65 ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:73 1e06137a29bb469e8d7bda7e82bbcbbb a10c3a6e8d4e462ba2ce1e211092ca7a
msgid "GPIO6～GPIO11 被内置 flash 占用，不可用做它用；"
msgstr "GPIO6～GPIO11 are occupied by the built-in flash and cannot be used for other purposes;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:66 c479901bd78746a3a23a0a8bf31e3708
msgid "GPIO34，35，36 和 39 为 input only pin 脚，不具备 output 能力"
msgstr "GPIO34, GPIO35, GPIO36, and GPIO39 are input-only pins and do not have output capability;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:67 ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:76 71c1c4b4da394a0fb576dd23b0e354c8 aee2fa94a0074238b350acf50437a117
msgid "ESP32 内置 GPIO 矩阵，部分外设接口可以配置到任意空闲 pin 脚上，即硬件设计时，不需要严格将某些功能固定在某些 pin 脚上。"
msgstr "ESP32 has a built-in GPIO matrix. Some peripheral interfaces can be configured to any free pin. Therefore, in hardware design, certain functions do not have to be strictly fixed to certain pins."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:69 ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:78 0db2e216edba4cd3988e2becfc158073 3739e5f4939440dc9cdbe45fbd81267f
msgid "详细信息可以参考 `ESP32 datasheet <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_datasheet_cn.pdf>`_ 中表格 9 的内容。"
msgstr "For details, refer to Table 9 in the `ESP32 datasheet <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_datasheet_cn.pdf>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:71 05607adb0ba54f62891e80649a6e4a87
msgid "WROVER／WROVER-I／WROVER-B／WROVER-IB 共有 24 个 pin 脚可供客户使用，注意事项如下："
msgstr "WROVER/WROVER-I/WROVER-B/WROVER-IB provide 24 pins for customer use. Notes:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:74 5c114f026cbd4cd49f450ff4cf64d0ec
msgid "GPIO34，35，36 和 39 为 input only pin 脚，不具备 output 能力；"
msgstr "GPIO34, GPIO35, GPIO36, and GPIO39 are input-only pins and do not have output capability;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:75 21ef0ee149144f548890f0b06bfbc7d8
msgid "WROVER 系列模组中，GPIO12 由于在模组内部被上拉，不建议用做触摸传感功能；"
msgstr "In WROVER series modules, GPIO12 is pulled up inside the module and is not recommended for touch sensor functions;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:80 2962da9ad8374855b426291d5ae8927f
msgid "ESP32 有 3 组 UART，但下载只可使用 UART0，且 pin 脚固定"
msgstr "ESP32 has three UART groups, but downloading can only use UART0, and the pins are fixed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:85 ffd50a9b25d541a9be5da6a6c71bf740
msgid "ESP32 是否支持 A2DP 发送音频？"
msgstr "Does ESP32 support A2DP audio transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:87 dde56e016a3045a082f77a3dcf818b47
msgid "ESP32 支持 A2DP 发送音频，可参考例程 `a2dp_source <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/d85d3d969ff4b42e2616fd40973d637ff337fae6/examples/bluetooth/bluedroid/classic_bt/a2dp_source#esp-idf-a2dp-source-demo>`_。"
msgstr "ESP32 supports A2DP audio transmission. Refer to the example `a2dp_source <https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/d85d3d969ff4b42e2616fd40973d637ff337fae6/examples/bluetooth/bluedroid/classic_bt/a2dp_source#esp-idf-a2dp-source-demo>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:92 6802bb0ac9704c30a7730172c8ac4005
msgid "ESP8266 I2C 是软件模拟的吗？"
msgstr "Is ESP8266 I2C implemented by software simulation?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:94 d1895f80589c468cbbded164dcbe6262
msgid "ESP8266 I2C 是使用 gpio 软件模拟。"
msgstr "ESP8266 I2C is implemented by GPIO software simulation."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:99 eda182141e704bbc85d55d153a527edc
msgid "使用 ESP8266-NONOS-V3.0 版本的 SDK，如下报错是什么原因？"
msgstr "When using ESP8266-NONOS-V3.0 SDK, what causes the following error?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:105 60e9669ed57a4e658b71ea95e472112d
msgid "导致 E:M 开头的 LOG  是内存不足的原因。"
msgstr "Logs beginning with E:M are caused by insufficient memory."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:110 676cd66d9b2c48379c1f77bf1ccd61f8
msgid "ESP8266 PWM 频率范围是多少呢？"
msgstr "What is the PWM frequency range of ESP8266?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:112 2db19efefa314c5eb86660920df03227
msgid "ESP8266 PWM 是软件模拟的，受定时器限制 CLK 最大为 1M。推荐频率为 1K，也可以通过降低占空比分辨率的方式提高频率。"
msgstr "ESP8266 PWM is implemented by software simulation and is limited by the timer. The maximum CLK is 1M. The recommended frequency is 1K. The frequency can also be increased by reducing duty-cycle resolution."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:117 3d7d02c7964947999064153d24f6bc25
msgid "ESP32 GPIO 管脚输出 PWM 存在限制吗？"
msgstr "Are there any restrictions on ESP32 GPIO PWM output?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:119 d5b782ee41f8412ebc6fef8cd8ce6425
msgid "ESP32 PWM 可通过 IO Matrix 切换至任意 GPIO 输出。但是由于 GPIO34 ~ GPIO39 仅为输入模式，故不支持做 PWM 输出。"
msgstr "ESP32 PWM can be switched to any GPIO output through the IO Matrix. However, GPIO34 ~ GPIO39 are input-only and therefore do not support PWM output."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:124 ee8589d2a8d14cf5acaa9511af1aeb4d
msgid "ESP32S2 Touch Sensor 的防水功能是在有水时屏蔽 Touch 还是有水时仍然能识别 Touch 事件？"
msgstr "For the waterproof function of ESP32S2 Touch Sensor, does it block Touch when water is present, or can it still recognize Touch events when water is present?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:126 567ee04ac51a4bd69b253e9ed13fcb45
msgid "当水对触摸传感器的影响较小时(水珠)，传感器会主动适应；当水对触摸传感器的影响较大时(水流)，传感器可通过软件配置来选择锁定某些传感器通道的状态来避免水的影响"
msgstr "When the impact of water on the touch sensor is small (water droplets), the sensor actively adapts. When the impact is large (water flow), the sensor can be configured by software to lock the status of certain sensor channels to avoid the influence of water."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:131 5b4e686057ec4bec9fe594be1020e5df
msgid "ESP32S2 Touch Sensor 的防水流功能在屏蔽有水流的 Touchpad 时，是否能够保持未沾水的 Pad 仍能使用？"
msgstr "When the ESP32S2 Touch Sensor water-flow waterproof function blocks a Touchpad with water flow, can pads without water still be used?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:133 251adf437d61408f90b9f1cc2bd79306
msgid "可以，可通过软件选择具体屏蔽的通道"
msgstr "Yes. Specific blocked channels can be selected through software."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:138 fe492508fe044621b1f9db0a859a579c
msgid "是否有推荐的可以用于 Touch Sensor 测试、稳定触发 Touch Sensor 并且参数与人手触摸时参数接近的材料？"
msgstr "Is there any recommended material for Touch Sensor testing that can trigger the Touch Sensor stably and has parameters close to those of human finger touch?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:140 416e63fedd4b499cac6e58df51a96cec
msgid "对一致性要求较高的实验可使用手机电容笔来替代人手进行测试"
msgstr "For experiments requiring high consistency, a capacitive stylus for mobile phones can be used instead of a human finger."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:145 1f454b86a2bf418e947544ff4866c48f
msgid "Touch Sensor 的 Pin 能否重映射？"
msgstr "Can Touch Sensor pins be remapped?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:147 c163cda3aacd431aafe936ae5d399e46
msgid "不能, 因为 Touch Sensor 属于模拟信号处理。"
msgstr "No, because Touch Sensor belongs to analog signal processing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:152 8dbd470dfa304e3c8b2ca5f2708d7ed0
msgid "在覆盖亚克力板后，Touch Sensor 检测阈值是否需要重新设置？"
msgstr "After covering with an acrylic plate, does the Touch Sensor detection threshold need to be reset?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:154 2762b18210084ac2ac52a3a481528c96
msgid "需要重新设置一个阈值"
msgstr "Yes, a new threshold needs to be set."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:159 3aa723fa3b77493e92c1fa1e48d3cf8b
msgid "Touch Sensor 能否检测是否有亚克力板覆盖，以便在添加或移除亚克力板时，自动切换预设定的检测阈值？"
msgstr "Can the Touch Sensor detect whether an acrylic plate is covered, so that preset detection thresholds can be automatically switched when the acrylic plate is added or removed?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:161 325c995e7b9248fb977b1013149d9be6
msgid "暂时不能自动适应覆盖层物理参数变化所带来的影响"
msgstr "Currently, it cannot automatically adapt to changes in physical parameters of the cover layer."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:166 04df134620b24b12b17b91f5a1db0526
msgid "ESP32 SD 卡支持的最大容量是多少？"
msgstr "What is the maximum SD card capacity supported by ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:168 24ba108ecf9e415796fb783978d21a6e
msgid "SD3.01 规范中 SDXC 的卡最大支持 2TB（2048GB）容量。"
msgstr "In the SD3.01 specification, SDXC cards support a maximum capacity of 2 TB (2048 GB)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:169 cb89e6583dc945f09d664f635fa0d182
msgid "ESP32 的 SDMMC host 符合 SD3.01 协议，通过该外设可以访问最多 2TB 的区域；使用 SDSPI 驱动通过 SPI 总线访问卡时，硬件也支持访问 2TB 的区域。"
msgstr "The ESP32 SDMMC host complies with the SD3.01 protocol and can access an area of up to 2 TB through this peripheral. When using the SDSPI driver to access the card through the SPI bus, the hardware also supports access to an area of 2 TB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:170 a73edf84678547d7af31aaa15f6445cf
msgid "在软件层面上，卡能使用的空间还受文件系统的影响。"
msgstr "At the software level, the usable space of the card is also affected by the file system."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:175 1de4ed45c77043339d22331c75032be0
msgid "ESP32 是否支持 USB 功能？"
msgstr "Does ESP32 support USB?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:177 359035fa2cd54cbb8e3217d4533617fe
msgid "ESP32 不支持 USB 功能。"
msgstr "ESP32 does not support USB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:178 560526ed363a4ef5bc1ce4a454a5452f
msgid "ESP32-S2 支持 USB1.1 。"
msgstr "ESP32-S2 supports USB 1.1."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:183 089ac6e7b49946d8b59b1ccb789995c6
msgid "ESP8266 使⽤ hw timer 中断有哪些注意事项？"
msgstr "What should be noted when using the hw timer interrupt on ESP8266?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:185 8f5a1c4b95b04779857204422e35df48
msgid "可以参考相关 API 文档  `ESP8266 技术参考手册 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266-technical_reference_cn.pdf>`__。"
msgstr "Refer to the relevant API documentation: `ESP8266 Technical Reference Manual <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266-technical_reference_cn.pdf>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:186 8f3e623e41994e6a92bd7cf8c3bc487b
msgid "如果使用 NONOS SDK 可以阅读  `ESP8266 Non-OS SDK API 参考 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/2c-esp8266_non_os_sdk_api_reference_cn.pdf>`__。"
msgstr "If using the NONOS SDK, read `ESP8266 Non-OS SDK API Reference <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/2c-esp8266_non_os_sdk_api_reference_cn.pdf>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:187 3b43358a30d8465fb069c4149a33d116
msgid "通常情况下，硬件中断需要尽快执行结束，并且将回调函数放入 IRAM 中，避免 Cache 影响。 - RTOS SDK 需要函数去添加 IRAM_ATTR - NonOS SDK 不能在函数前添加 ICACHE_FLASH_ATTR"
msgstr "Generally, hardware interrupts should finish execution as quickly as possible, and callback functions should be placed in IRAM to avoid cache effects. - RTOS SDK requires adding IRAM_ATTR to the function. - NonOS SDK must not add ICACHE_FLASH_ATTR before the function."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:194 d5eefcd98b704d2589e351fe6691be9e
msgid "ESP32 脉冲宽度调制（PWM）信号是否可以分配任意一个 I/O 上？"
msgstr "Can the ESP32 pulse width modulation (PWM) signal be assigned to any I/O?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:196 87887029577f4fc6a02b6e307b11ec6d
msgid "除了只有输⼊功能的 I/O（例如：GPIO34-GPIO39） 之外，理论上 PWM 可以输出到任何管脚。"
msgstr "Except for input-only I/Os (for example: GPIO34-GPIO39), PWM can theoretically be output to any pin."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:197 9b5c581a7702482a9cf4db6139f22a2b
msgid "实际使用中仍会受到模组与芯片限制，模组未引出管脚或 Flash 占用等情况影响。"
msgstr "In actual use, it is still subject to module and chip limitations, such as pins not being brought out by the module or pins being occupied by Flash."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:202 498d49366db24d959af4494022daabfe
msgid "ESP32 是否有 I2S 驱动 LCD 的参考代码？"
msgstr "Does ESP32 have reference code for driving an LCD with I2S?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:204 95181e43671e422389e1c3eb7a482d0d
msgid "I2S LCD driver：`esp-iot-solution i2s_devices <https://github.com/espressif/esp-iot-solution/tree/master/components/i2s_devices>`__。"
msgstr "I2S LCD driver: `esp-iot-solution i2s_devices <https://github.com/espressif/esp-iot-solution/tree/master/components/i2s_devices>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:209 d8d94623f8da425db9f68d9db78501de
msgid "ESP8266 RTOS_2.1 以及之前版本 SDK，如何将 LOG 配置到 UART1 ？"
msgstr "For ESP8266 RTOS_2.1 and earlier SDK versions, how can LOG be configured to UART1?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:211 c1daaf3109e641eea0fe6b9c0117790c
msgid "在配置 UART1 初始化后，可以通过 API 切换 LOG 输出到 UART1。"
msgstr "After configuring UART1 initialization, you can switch LOG output to UART1 through the API."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:220 b7075d68807c4ee0a69457fd9ec17bdf
msgid "使用 ESP8266 RTOS rel 3.0 以及之后的 SDK，如何将 LOG 配置到 UART1 ？"
msgstr "For ESP8266 RTOS rel 3.0 and later SDK versions, how can LOG be configured to UART1?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:222 0496fcfa887b49ed93ed25daf095769a
msgid "可通过  menuconfig -> Component config -> ESP8266-specific -> UART for console output -> custom -> UART peripheral to use for console output -> UART0 修改为 UART1 接口。"
msgstr "Use menuconfig -> Component config -> ESP8266-specific -> UART for console output -> custom -> UART peripheral to use for console output -> UART0, and change it to UART1."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:227 8a950a7b62f840b89b50e631fc19aee9
msgid "ESP32 IDF 中如何使能 UART 流控？"
msgstr "How to enable UART flow control in ESP32 IDF?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:229 ec27835656b64b29a35b722d069ac769
#, python-format
msgid "硬件流控使能： `uart-flow-control <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/peripherals/uart.html?highlight=uart%20flow%20control#multiple-steps>`__。"
msgstr "Enable hardware flow control: `uart-flow-control <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/peripherals/uart.html?highlight=uart%20flow%20control#multiple-steps>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:230 475190449fcb44c3a69146d98a266cab
#, python-format
msgid "软件流控使能： `software-flow-control <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/peripherals/uart.html?highlight=uart%20flow%20control#software-flow-control>`__。"
msgstr "Enable software flow control: `software-flow-control <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/peripherals/uart.html?highlight=uart%20flow%20control#software-flow-control>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:235 c88cd05b699b4e24b40c5ccd0d3d0231
msgid "ESP8266 NonOS SDK PWM 的变化缓慢，又哪些原因？"
msgstr "Why does the PWM of ESP8266 NonOS SDK change slowly?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:237 8f09f0ae51284acab26849f014d99c5d
msgid "如果使用 SDK example/IOT_demo 中的渐变 API，如 light_set_aim 或 light_set_aim_r 这些 API，需要渐变的过程。"
msgstr "If using gradient APIs in SDK example/IOT_demo, such as light_set_aim or light_set_aim_r, these APIs require a gradual transition process."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:238 c640ddf38fcf46988b5bd4018da767c7
msgid "若需要 PWM Duty 设置后⽴即⽣效，则可以调⽤接⼝ pwm_set_duty，需要注意调⽤ pwm_set_duty 后要调⽤ pwm_start 此次设置才能⽣效。"
msgstr "If the PWM duty needs to take effect immediately after being set, call the interface pwm_set_duty. Note that after calling pwm_set_duty, pwm_start must be called for this setting to take effect."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:243 6c99a03a58854187a816f7cb7d51c162
msgid "ESP8266 部分 GPIO 出现高电平 ？"
msgstr "Why do some ESP8266 GPIOs output a high level?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:245 5082ddd8f0f14fefa29a06fa60551e0e
msgid "根据硬件设计，部分 GPIO 存在默认上下拉状态，所以在系统初始化时，该管脚的电平状态不受程序控制，所以会出现程序在引导过程中部分 GPIO 电平不正确。"
msgstr "According to the hardware design, some GPIOs have default pull-up/pull-down states. During system initialization, the pin level is not controlled by the program, so some GPIO levels may be incorrect during program boot."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:246 d36ab38ad2214cb9b4aedfb838f3fc24
msgid "如果需要使用这些 GPIO ，硬件上建议外接器件与默认上下拉电平一致，软件可以在 bootloader 过程中调整电平状态，软件方法也会存在短暂电平异常。"
msgstr "If these GPIOs need to be used, it is recommended that the external hardware devices match the default pull-up/pull-down level. Software can adjust the level during the bootloader process, but the software method may also cause a short abnormal level."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:251 5a2d4bd633464fab9f3437a9084cc915
msgid "ESP8266 ADC 的精度如何？"
msgstr "What is the accuracy of ESP8266 ADC?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:253 c6b30da164a54bd38b9bddbd44fbaa05
msgid "ESP8266 ADC 为 10 bit, 理论精度为 2^10=1024。"
msgstr "ESP8266 ADC is 10-bit, and the theoretical accuracy is 2^10=1024."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:254 8c98d00481f642ae8f85e04e8797df91
msgid "ESP8266 连接路由器后，单 STA 模式会进⼊ modem-sleep，导致芯⽚内部参考值变化，因此 ADC 测量得数据变化。"
msgstr "After ESP8266 connects to a router, single STA mode enters modem-sleep, causing the internal reference value of the chip to change, so ADC measurement data changes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:255 fa02f6ddb35c40ac8eeb1d90074658d2
msgid "如果想要测量精确，可以再关闭 wifi 后，使用 `system_adc_fast_read` 函数读取。"
msgstr "For accurate measurement, turn off Wi-Fi and use the `system_adc_fast_read` function to read."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:260 e4ba1bb584d5418ea624f048b65a684c
msgid "ESP8266 如何获取 ADC 寄存器 bitmap 信息？"
msgstr "How can ESP8266 obtain ADC register bitmap information?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:262 b78cf7a477b940e0b8db9d52b02222bf
msgid "由于 ESP8266 ADC 是和内部 RF 电路⾼度集成的，所以 bitmap 和寄存器信息没有公开，如有特殊需求请联系 sales@espressif.com。"
msgstr "Since the ESP8266 ADC is highly integrated with the internal RF circuit, bitmap and register information are not public. If there are special requirements, please contact sales@espressif.com."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:267 8b32706196fe4512b810e88391367f73
msgid "ESP32 ADC 有⼏个通道？采样率和有效位数是多少？"
msgstr "How many ADC channels does ESP32 have? What are the sampling rate and effective number of bits?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:269 863c7414f65e4bdca3bca48920fb7fac
msgid "ESP32 的 ADC 共有 18 个通道。"
msgstr "ESP32 has 18 ADC channels."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:270 d98e2925ddb04697b8e63028e41b2894
msgid "在停⽌ Wi-Fi 的情况下，采样率能达到每秒 100000 次。"
msgstr "When Wi-Fi is stopped, the sampling rate can reach 100,000 samples per second."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:271 9f5f719018244daab06e5cbb5f54f4d9
msgid "在 Wi-Fi 正常⼯作的情况下，能达到每秒 1000 次。"
msgstr "When Wi-Fi works normally, it can reach 1,000 samples per second."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:272 ccaeeeb1f0eb42d19e7028ac5f2f0ad2
msgid "ADC 内部有效位数为 12 位。"
msgstr "The internal effective number of ADC bits is 12 bits."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:277 f33dd4033c3d419ea357a8505e29e52d
msgid "ESP32 是否可以关闭线程调度使用一个单独的 CPU 以实现实时 GPIO？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 disable thread scheduling and use one separate CPU to implement real-time GPIO?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:279 74a5fdffda1e4049830671baab347feb
msgid "目前 SDK 没有相关的配置选择供 CPU1 单独运行，两个核心只支持 SMP，不支持 AMP。"
msgstr "The current SDK does not provide a configuration option for CPU1 to run separately. The two cores only support SMP and do not support AMP."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:280 fad2d072277e40858410c6fb23ce3a19
msgid "解决输出波形被打断的问题有以下解决方案:"
msgstr "Solutions for the issue where the output waveform is interrupted include:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:282 0c36cb6956aa49c8a54367387c16bb59
msgid "使用硬件的信号输出，选择相关数字协议实现 SPI， I2C, I2S 等, 特殊用法 SPI 取信号输出线产生波形。"
msgstr "Use hardware signal output and select relevant digital protocols such as SPI, I2C, and I2S. For special usage, SPI can be used to generate waveforms on signal output lines."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:283 8237de90fdc44311937345a9125d0d6e
msgid "硬件 RMT 是否可以产生想要的波形， 并达到足够的长度 。"
msgstr "Check whether hardware RMT can generate the desired waveform and reach sufficient length."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:284 03f9c9772bad40b1a12bce88d475961d
msgid "硬件中断中产生相应波形，需要将所有回调放入 IRAM 中。"
msgstr "Generate corresponding waveforms in hardware interrupts, and place all callbacks in IRAM."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:285 bb19b6212935431c833a2648cf7f4888
msgid "可以利用芯片中的协处理器，它可以当作无操作系统的单片机，但目前只支持汇编语言。"
msgstr "Use the coprocessor in the chip. It can be used as an MCU without an operating system, but currently only assembly language is supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:290 4d154d73130545e898a652b20da2a5a5
msgid "ESP32 Touch 应用有哪些参考资料？"
msgstr "What reference materials are available for ESP32 Touch applications?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:292 eecc1211b6ed448383d53c8f09104f17
msgid "ESP32 touch 应用可以参考 `Touch 软硬件设计 <https://github.com/espressif/esp-iot-solution/tree/master/examples/touch_pad_evb>`__ 。"
msgstr "ESP32 touch applications can refer to `Touch software and hardware design <https://github.com/espressif/esp-iot-solution/tree/master/examples/touch_pad_evb>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:298 45279499b14f4f1db4208952766fb268
msgid "ESP32 SD 卡是否可以与 Flash & Psram 共同使用？"
msgstr "Can the ESP32 SD card be used together with Flash & PSRAM?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:300 c85d63233571452c8b2266debe9ebaa2
msgid "可以共同使用。"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:301 97df7260a93c4ce3be5ec72f64ab152c
msgid "ESP32 Flash & PSRAM 与 SD 卡使用的不是同一组 SDIO。"
msgstr "ESP32 Flash & PSRAM and the SD card do not use the same SDIO group."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:306 900ddce9909543759da5666584928a6f
msgid "ESP32 使用 UART0 作为通信串口，有哪些？"
msgstr "What should be noted when using UART0 on ESP32 as a communication serial port?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:308 971dd96d59b440118fcc808ba0f0f3eb
msgid "通常情况下不建议将 UART0 作为普通的通信串口，因为 UART0 为设备默认 LOG 输出串口。"
msgstr "Generally, it is not recommended to use UART0 as a normal communication serial port, because UART0 is the default LOG output serial port of the device."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:309 df6e58bd620341cfbe0bede6a88f31c2
msgid "若 ESP32 的 UART 不够用，或者硬件设计已经不方便更改的情况下，如果您要使用 UART0 作为普通的通信串口，请参考以下建议："
msgstr "If ESP32 UARTs are insufficient, or the hardware design is already inconvenient to change, and UART0 must be used as a normal communication serial port, refer to the following suggestions:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:311 8cd3a1f6bf8b40779419a819e28d41d7
msgid "**软件方面**：防止打印影响串口通信，默认程序中 UART0 主要有三处打印设置"
msgstr "**Software**: To prevent prints from affecting serial communication, there are mainly three print settings for UART0 in the default program:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:313 b10fdc22cc2943ebb8c5149fe0103a34
msgid "第一处是上电 ROM 打印，上电时可将 MTDO pin 设为低电平屏蔽上电 ROM 打印。"
msgstr "The first is power-on ROM printing. During power-on, set the MTDO pin to low level to suppress power-on ROM printing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:314 94b90f33d9d24fd283481b4628fbeb32
msgid "第二处是 bootloader log 信息输出，您可以将 menuconfig -> Bootloader config -> Bootloader log verbosity 设置为 No output 来屏蔽 bootloader log 输出。"
msgstr "The second is bootloader log output. Set menuconfig -> Bootloader config -> Bootloader log verbosity to No output to suppress bootloader log output."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:315 857506d4c23a42dcb6544ffd7f351599
msgid "第三处是 app log 信息输出，您可以将 menuconfig -> Component config -> Log output -> Default log verbosity 设置为 No output 来屏蔽 log 输出。"
msgstr "The third is app log output. Set menuconfig -> Component config -> Log output -> Default log verbosity to No output to suppress log output."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:317 e8b5f74dfc9c442e857ee2f1cf530c6e
msgid "**硬件方面**："
msgstr "**Hardware**:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:319 f79436134a2248f68a8b9b9eeaeeadc8
msgid "在下载程序的时候，注意防止 UART0 上有其它设备，如果有其它设备可能会影响程序的下载。建议在 ESP32 和其它设备之间预留一个 0 Ω 电阻，如果下载有问题可以断开这个 0 Ω 电阻。"
msgstr "When downloading programs, ensure that there are no other devices on UART0. If other devices are present, they may affect program downloading. It is recommended to reserve a 0 Ω resistor between ESP32 and other devices. If downloading has problems, disconnect this 0 Ω resistor."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:324 f0f10fe22988403e9a6a3ade00e729c5
msgid "ESP32-SOLO-1 的 GPIO34-GPIO39 是否可作为 UART 的 RX 及 CAN 的 RX 信号管脚？"
msgstr "Can GPIO34-GPIO39 of ESP32-SOLO-1 be used as UART RX and CAN RX signal pins?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:326 c4bd9a96e57942e28bc589669af85f14
msgid "GPIO34-GPIO39 仅作为接收，可作为 UART 的 RX 及 CAN 的 RX 信号管脚。"
msgstr "GPIO34-GPIO39 are input-only and can be used as UART RX and CAN RX signal pins."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:331 4172160c98dc43ed988c678d4cbd8548
msgid "使用 ESP-WROOM-S2 模组，是否支持 SDIO 作从机？"
msgstr "Does the ESP-WROOM-S2 module support SDIO as a slave?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:333 65f5721d5a8140d3aef10de787561302
msgid "ESP-WROOM-S2 的 Flash 使用的是 SPI 的接口，故支持 SDIO 作从机。"
msgstr "ESP-WROOM-S2 Flash uses an SPI interface, so SDIO as a slave is supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:338 cd562df04aa94fd1bc76ba30ee029d74
msgid "ESP32 是否支持使用晶振作为 I2S 的时钟源？"
msgstr "Does ESP32 support using a crystal oscillator as the I2S clock source?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:340 0f06d610cad9459abead76aa4aca9183
msgid "ESP32 不支持使用晶振作为 I2S 的时钟源，可阅读 `《ESP32 技术参考手册》 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_technical_reference_manual_cn.pdf>`__  来了解 I2S 的时钟源配置。"
msgstr "ESP32 does not support using a crystal oscillator as the I2S clock source. Read the `ESP32 Technical Reference Manual <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_technical_reference_manual_cn.pdf>`__ to learn about I2S clock source configuration."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:345 8add793fb9824792863dad0a94e7f32f
msgid "使用 ESP8266 调用 adc_read_fast() API 会导致 WiFi 断连？"
msgstr "Will calling the adc_read_fast() API on ESP8266 cause Wi-Fi disconnection?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:347 2981254d296f4d95bd8a8fea68d1589c
msgid "调用 adc_read_fast() API 前需要将 Wi-Fi 和中断关闭，可参见此 API 的 `使用说明 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/api-reference/peripherals/adc.html?highlight=adc_read#_CPPv413adc_read_fastP8uint16_t8uint16_t>`__ 。"
msgstr "Before calling the adc_read_fast() API, Wi-Fi and interrupts need to be disabled. Refer to the `usage description of this API <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/api-reference/peripherals/adc.html?highlight=adc_read#_CPPv413adc_read_fastP8uint16_t8uint16_t>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:348 18346fd7eb8d42a4a32b71de35222770
msgid "由于adc_read_fast() API 会进行连续采集，ADC 内部与 Wi-Fi RF 存在耦合部分，无法在 Wi-Fi 开启的状态下调用该函数。"
msgstr "Since adc_read_fast() performs continuous sampling, and the ADC is internally coupled with Wi-Fi RF, this function cannot be called when Wi-Fi is enabled."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:349 fd3fb4134bc74dbda180a56eeb1de322
msgid "在 Wi-Fi 开启的时候请使用 adc_read() API 进行 ADC 采集，并且将为保证数据稳定，需要使用 esp_wifi_set_ps(WIFI_PS_NONE);  关闭 Wi-Fi 调制解调休眠。"
msgstr "When Wi-Fi is enabled, use adc_read() API for ADC sampling. To ensure stable data, call esp_wifi_set_ps(WIFI_PS_NONE); to disable Wi-Fi modem sleep."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:350 fc9cbb3359d74d9491f93e6ee6daada4
msgid "备注：ADC 采样率：在停⽌ Wi-Fi 的情况下，能达到每秒 100000 次。Wi-Fi 正常⼯作的情况下，能达到每秒 1000 次。"
msgstr "Note: ADC sampling rate: when Wi-Fi is stopped, it can reach 100,000 samples per second. When Wi-Fi is working normally, it can reach 1,000 samples per second."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:355 8b46cbb43922424fa59549cf4e651b3d
msgid "使用 ESP32 如何动态修改串口波特率并立即生效？"
msgstr "How to dynamically modify the UART baud rate on ESP32 and make it take effect immediately?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:357 9cd1c23b8bcb4a5eb6ad53bd084917db
msgid "请使用 uart_set_baudrate() API 来修改 UART 波特率 。 参见 `此 API 说明 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/peripherals/uart.html?highlight=uart_set_baud#_CPPv417uart_get_baudrate11uart_port_tP8uint32_t>`__ 。"
msgstr "Use the uart_set_baudrate() API to modify the UART baud rate. Refer to the API documentation: `uart_set_baudrate <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/peripherals/uart.html?highlight=uart_set_baud#_CPPv417uart_get_baudrate11uart_port_tP8uint32_t>`__"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:362 30a2f00fe23f4962939ebace49d07f34
msgid "ESP32-S2 取消了 SDIO 接口，是否还支持外接 TF 卡？"
msgstr "ESP32-S2 has removed the SDIO interface. Does it still support external TF cards?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:364 ebb3b40df8d64b8898797e1df9dea69d
msgid "ESP32-S2 有 4 组 SPI 的接口，可使用 SPI2/SPI3 的接口外接 TF 卡，当使用 SPI2/SPI3 的接口外接 TF 卡时，SPI 应设为通用 SPI 模式。"
msgstr "ESP32-S2 has four SPI interfaces. You can use SPI2 or SPI3 to connect an external TF card. When using SPI2 or SPI3 to connect a TF card, SPI should be configured as general-purpose SPI mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:369 afa72c814f70453c8aeba0df7fd69d5a
msgid "ESP32 GPIO 电平翻转速度是多少？"
msgstr "What is the GPIO level toggle speed of ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:371 97aecca248c84400b8b97a1268f48d68
msgid "GPIO 电平翻转大约耗时 300ns。"
msgstr "GPIO level toggling takes approximately 300 ns."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:376 31fcfb2045f94c9aad4955412fba04f2
msgid "ESP32 如何连接 MIC？"
msgstr "How to connect a MIC to ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:378 652de8a69d734009807df9aeec2ef29d
msgid "如果连接数字 MIC ，可以连接 I2S 外设。"
msgstr "For a digital MIC, connect it to the I2S peripheral."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:379 2f56688a6308439b9c022a084a9b0f4d
msgid "如果连接模拟 MIC ，可以连接 ADC 外设。"
msgstr "For an analog MIC, connect it to the ADC peripheral."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:384 0c34b5c76ea9479fabb66025df8d202c
msgid "ESP32 是否支持模拟音频或是数字音频输出？"
msgstr "Does ESP32 support analog or digital audio output?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:386 6dc87c8f36a34951bdfd9c6a53a6e769
msgid "ESP32 支持 DAC 模拟音频输出，可以使用它播放提示音等简单音频，但是如果用它播放音乐，音乐效果不是很好。"
msgstr "ESP32 supports DAC analog audio output. It can be used to play prompt tones or simple audio, but the audio quality is not very good for music playback."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:387 94cd2b54a90f412e9f858a5098c7ab00
msgid "ESP32 同时支持 I2S 数字音频输出，I2S 可配置引脚可以在 `ESP32 datasheet <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_datasheet_cn.pdf>`_ 第四章查看。"
msgstr "ESP32 also supports I2S digital audio output. The configurable I2S pins can be found in Chapter 4 of the `ESP32 datasheet <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_datasheet_cn.pdf>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:392 7ede0b00be074a468832cd61bd80b225
msgid "ESP32 中 SPI/HSPI/VSPI 三者有什么区别呢？"
msgstr "What is the difference between SPI, HSPI, and VSPI on ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:394 1bddb25e2e1a4360921277dc44827f3c
msgid "`并行 QSPI` 接口中 SPI/HSPI/VSPI 是连接外部 Flash 的分组，默认 Flash 挂载在 SPI 分组上。"
msgstr "In the parallel QSPI interface, SPI/HSPI/VSPI are groups used to connect external Flash. By default, Flash is mounted on the SPI group."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:395 e93e03431d64400a8208a4b4ab43ccfe
msgid "驱动中可以任意调用的 HSPI/VSPI 均为通用 SPI，名称中的差异仅用以分组之间的区分。"
msgstr "In the driver, HSPI and VSPI that can be freely called are both general-purpose SPI interfaces. The name difference is only used to distinguish between groups."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:400 da9e650a4743469a94fbc79555c44acb
msgid "ESP32 当⼀些 RTC 外设的电源打开时（SARADC1、SARADC2、AMP、HALL 传感器），GPIO36 和 GPIO39 的数字输⼊会被拉低约 80 ns，如何解决？"
msgstr "When some RTC peripheral power domains are enabled on ESP32, GPIO36 and GPIO39 digital inputs are pulled low for about 80 ns. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:402 36b1a6b2a88a4ee797ca94a32879035c
msgid "当⽤户决定把⽤于控制以上传感器的电源域打开时，应当忽略来⾃ GPIO36 和 GPIO39 的输⼊。"
msgstr "When users decide to enable the power domains used to control the following sensors: SARADC1, SARADC2, AMP, Hall sensor, the input from GPIO36 and GPIO39 should be ignored."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:407 232cb2e9d009462daf4a7859605d6d9d
msgid "ESP32 LEDC 递减渐变，duty 值溢出错误，如何解决？"
msgstr "How to solve the ESP32 LEDC decreasing fade duty overflow error?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:409 3259a71203ec4bf1a3ca9eb4515829e8
msgid "使⽤ LEDC 的过程中，应避免以下三个条件同时成⽴："
msgstr "When using LEDC, avoid the following three conditions occurring at the same time:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:411 f7a06b9647e447409d5e4b71fc94b235
msgid "LEDC 启动递减渐变功能；"
msgstr "LEDC decreasing fade function is enabled;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:412 7aada901011b4863b6ebc1ed8700d00e
msgid "LEDC 渐变过程中 scale 寄存器设置为 1；"
msgstr "During LEDC fading, the scale register is set to 1;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:413 eb4240a2aff6479483ed258fb5e3cd08
msgid "LEDC 递减渐变开始时刻或者过程中的某⼀时刻，duty 值为 2 :sup:`LEDC_HSTIMERx_DUTY_RES` 或 2 :sup:`LEDC_LSTIMERx_DUTY_RES`"
msgstr "At the start of the decreasing fade, or at some point during the fade, the duty value is 2 :sup:`LEDC_HSTIMERx_DUTY_RES` or 2 :sup:`LEDC_LSTIMERx_DUTY_RES`"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:418 3dce1d5c0e9146b1aa03b969b4e08aab
msgid "ESP32 当 CAN 控制器处于复位模式（即 RESET_MODE 位置 1 或由于总线关闭）或总线关闭恢复状态时，接收错误计数器 (REC) 的数值仍会变化，如何解决？"
msgstr "When the ESP32 CAN controller is in reset mode or bus-off recovery state, REC still changes. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:420 32165eb18335485eaa27cf91fd33614f
msgid "进⼊复位模式时，应将 ``LISTEN_ONLY_MODE`` 置位，此时 REC 数值不会变化。退出复位模式前或总线关闭恢复完成时，再恢复正常的操作模式。"
msgstr "When entering reset mode, set ``LISTEN_ONLY_MODE``. In this case, the REC value will not change. Before exiting reset mode or after bus-off recovery is complete, restore the normal operation mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:425 92396877361a4914a80d31dc2735290f
msgid "ESP32 当 CAN 控制器处于总线关闭恢复过程中时，必须等待总线上出现 128 次总线空闲信号（连续 11 个隐性位），才能再次进⼊主动错误状态，如何解决？"
msgstr "During ESP32 CAN bus-off recovery, the controller must wait for 128 bus idle signals before re-entering the error-active state. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:427 2dd7989b63214d9f9a2c5796277fca06
msgid "在总线关闭恢复过程中，错误报警限制中断并不⼀定指示恢复过程已完成。⽤户需检查 ``STATUS_NODE_BUS_OFF`` 位来验证恢复过程是否完成。"
msgstr "During bus-off recovery, the error warning limit interrupt does not necessarily indicate that the recovery process is complete. Users need to check the ``STATUS_NODE_BUS_OFF`` bit to verify whether the recovery process has completed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:432 3557f461a14c4cbb8cc096f6c7db2fc9
msgid "ESP32 总线关闭恢复完成后，CAN 控制器下⼀次发送的数据可能出错（即不符合 CAN 数据帧格式），如何解决？"
msgstr "After ESP32 CAN bus-off recovery is complete, the next transmitted frame may be incorrect. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:434 736901dc0a704c0581799a46059fdb36
msgid "⼀旦通过错误报警限制中断检测到总线关闭恢复完成，CAN 控制器应先进⼊复位模式来复位控制器的内部信号，随后退出复位模式。"
msgstr "Once bus-off recovery completion is detected through the error warning limit interrupt, the CAN controller should first enter reset mode to reset internal controller signals, and then exit reset mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:439 a4cbecd10a514da296d52fe70016af05
msgid "ESP32 CAN 接收到错误的数据帧可能导致下⼀次接收到的数据字节⽆效，如何解决？"
msgstr "ESP32 CAN may receive an erroneous data frame, causing the next received data byte to be invalid. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:441 ce08af07103f42dea684ec82fde427e6
msgid "⽤户可以通过置位 INTERRUPT_BUS_ERR_INT_ENA 并在接收到总线错误中断时，读取 ``ERROR_CODE_CAPTURE_REG`` 来检测错误类型及错误位置。如果符合错误产⽣条件（在数据段或 CRC 字段发⽣位错误或填充错误），可以采⽤以下两种解决⽅法："
msgstr "Users can enable ``INTERRUPT_BUS_ERR_INT_ENA`` and read ``ERROR_CODE_CAPTURE_REG`` when a bus error interrupt is received to detect the error type and error location. If the error condition is met, such as a bit error or stuff error occurring in the data field or CRC field, the following two solutions can be used:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:443 28d92da2ff274660bb4787d4d2538716
msgid "CAN 控制器可以发送 0 字节的空数据帧来复位 CAN 控制器的内部信号。建议给空数据帧分配⼀个不会被任何 CAN 总线上的节点接收的 ID。"
msgstr "The CAN controller can send a 0-byte empty data frame to reset the internal signals of the CAN controller. It is recommended to assign the empty data frame an ID that will not be received by any node on the CAN bus."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:444 7be10679a77a4282a18c6e21082686ab
msgid "硬件复位 CAN 控制器（需要保存并恢复当前寄存器的数值）。"
msgstr "Hardware-reset the CAN controller. The current register values need to be saved and restored."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:449 4292e04f86bb407ca8ae076f0795b1c7
msgid "ESP32 如果多个 GPIO 管脚配置了沿中断，则硬件可能⽆法正确触发中断。"
msgstr "If multiple GPIO pins on ESP32 are configured with edge interrupts, the hardware may fail to trigger interrupts correctly."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:451 50abb031dbf7447c854135812808ab56
msgid "解决⽅法 1："
msgstr "Solution 1:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:453 e06a9e457e184482abe36efc650ef140
msgid "要实现 GPIO 的上升沿中断，按照下⾯的步骤实现："
msgstr "To implement a GPIO rising-edge interrupt, follow these steps:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:455 b76ab675759a4effac9f6feda2fc0ad9
msgid "配置 GPIO 的中断类型为⾼；"
msgstr "Configure the GPIO interrupt type as high level."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:456 ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:462 349bb13be9f2456aa82b0694421bb2cc c0463a2755904a9382c082edd5a12215
msgid "配置 CPU 的中断类型为 edge；"
msgstr "Configure the CPU interrupt type as edge."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:457 6ed84e2110f24d5982cd9681d1c93945
msgid "CPU 的中断服务响应后，把 GPIO 的中断类型改为低。此时会发⽣第⼆次中断，需要 CPU 忽略这次中断服务程序。"
msgstr "After the CPU interrupt service routine responds, change the GPIO interrupt type to low level. A second interrupt will occur at this time, and the CPU needs to ignore this ISR."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:459 98724e80181048e0a3fd924c370ebb00
msgid "同理，要实现 GPIO 的下降沿中断，则按如下步骤进⾏配置："
msgstr "Similarly, to implement a GPIO falling-edge interrupt, configure it as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:461 59e2418da15f4419aa28a8d2ee6af006
msgid "配置 GPIO 的中断类型为低；"
msgstr "Configure the GPIO interrupt type as low level."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:463 a31c827da69c41c591edd60da6f96221
msgid "CPU 的中断服务响应后，把 GPIO 的中断类型改为⾼。此时会发⽣第⼆次中断，需要 CPU 忽略这次中断服务程序。"
msgstr "After the CPU interrupt service routine responds, change the GPIO interrupt type to high level. A second interrupt will occur at this time, and the CPU needs to ignore this ISR."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:465 eea38e7c55cd4145b84bda80db2b997a
msgid "解决⽅法 2："
msgstr "Solution 2:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:467 37b48141f4bd42cfae56a1f4c9b6062a
msgid "假设 GPIO0 ~ GPIO31 为 Group1，GPIO32 ~ GPIO39 为 Group2，则："
msgstr "Assume GPIO0 ~ GPIO31 are Group1, and GPIO32 ~ GPIO39 are Group2:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:469 fcf04923a03e49eba6dbd4067b729c7d
msgid "⼀个 group 中同时只能有⼀个沿中断；如果有⼀个沿中断，则不能有电平中断。"
msgstr "Only one edge interrupt can exist in one group at the same time. If there is one edge interrupt, there cannot be any level interrupt."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:470 da1f9c8ea1e7415e9eb38346d0fd2c5c
msgid "⼀个 group 中如果没有沿中断，则可以有多组电平中断。"
msgstr "If there is no edge interrupt in a group, multiple level interrupts are allowed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:475 212779bd863d4bd0b8fdb8ba021939c9
msgid "ESP8266 可以实现脉冲计数吗？"
msgstr "Can ESP8266 implement pulse counting?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:477 fe5eb8cbcdd44c9a8f719e8ab065a03c
msgid "ESP8266 未包含硬件脉冲计数模块，所以仅支持通过 GPIO 上升沿或下降沿中断实现脉冲计数。"
msgstr "ESP8266 does not include a hardware pulse counter module, so it only supports pulse counting through GPIO rising-edge or falling-edge interrupts."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:478 90c559f386b54b1fafaaa39cc7bfd330
msgid "ESP8266 芯片中 Wi-Fi 开启后由于优先级太高可能会导致 GPIO 采样出现真空，中断采集的计数丢数据。"
msgstr "After Wi-Fi is enabled on ESP8266, GPIO sampling gaps may occur due to the high priority of Wi-Fi, which may cause missed counts during interrupt-based sampling."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:479 124d5a6847624fc3a2572696497cfcd4
msgid "综上，在计数要求较为严格的场景推荐使用 ESP32 以及后续推出的芯片。"
msgstr "Therefore, for scenarios with strict counting requirements, ESP32 and later chips are recommended."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:482 ad545d28aebb43f1aaa65daaebabbc42
msgid "请问一下ESP-01S模组与单片机通信的时候EN是否需要接上拉，还是内部已经做好上拉了"
msgstr "Does the EN pin need an external pull-up when ESP-01S communicates with an MCU, or is it already pulled up internally?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:483 2dfb91b21b214f63aa6387c47525731c
msgid "内部已做好上拉"
msgstr "It already has an internal pull-up."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:486 d8bf819dcdf84386bb0bc5bd76f7858c
msgid "ESP8266AT固件支持读取AD管脚的值吗"
msgstr "Does ESP8266 AT firmware support reading the ADC pin value?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:487 3c8580f68d624491ae93a61cdddd900c
msgid "支持，有对应的指令"
msgstr "Yes, corresponding AT commands are available."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:491 8012070df7e246319b55fe383a80faa1
msgid "ESP-12F可以接几个小的OLED屏幕"
msgstr "How many small OLED screens can ESP-12F connect to?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:492 4142dc18b2a94ca29db0cf2a5a748eb3
msgid "只能接一个"
msgstr "Only one."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:495 3726c69e7d5a4da7b9b8df4f0d31a38f
msgid "ESP8266模块具有RS232通讯功能吗"
msgstr "Does the ESP8266 module support RS232 communication?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:496 b2480780e70641278d98deb88255b57f
msgid "默认不支持RS232通讯，需要购买电平转换器进行转换、"
msgstr "RS232 communication is not supported by default. A level converter is required."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:499 6cf0ec0320d04e739cb456454d64ea7a
msgid "请问ESP-12F模组可以作为MCU进行开发么？"
msgstr "Can the ESP-12F module be developed as an MCU?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:500 43f87e4960664fabb774117244e78824
msgid "可以的，内置MCU的；"
msgstr "Yes. It has a built-in MCU."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:503 073b9d9aadb745c1b43351d15f6fe4c3
msgid "ESP-01S支持手机摄像头吗"
msgstr "Does ESP-01S support mobile phone cameras?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:504 f556fb8a8717458790e623a8890d1d84
msgid "模块不支持手机摄像头"
msgstr "No. The module does not support mobile phone cameras."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:507 9f2f60defc6443b8b7455cdf6d965280
msgid "ESP-07S和12S模组的RST，ADC需要拉电阻吗"
msgstr "Do the RST and ADC pins of ESP-07S and ESP-12S require resistors?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:508 8824cef403c445ae97065a90e0c6ce74
msgid "这两个引脚不需要拉"
msgstr "No pull resistors are required for these two pins."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:511 ec09ba8c4b6f4066895afb4bd04ec480
msgid "请问ESP-12F模组的ADC是否出厂就已经校准了的？"
msgstr "Is the ADC of ESP-12F calibrated before leaving the factory?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:512 0ba4dee5b9694af8a9c3d4e3c57b605a
msgid "是的，出厂芯片做了校准"
msgstr "Yes. The chip is calibrated before leaving the factory."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:515 c19820e486984445935aa4e6f98c1cc4
msgid "ESP-07S模组可以转有线网么？"
msgstr "Can ESP-07S convert to wired Ethernet?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:516 a66da95253aa4db383759a80549c65b8
msgid "没有以太网接口；"
msgstr "No. It does not have an Ethernet interface."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:519 b8fb1e7f26f14c889fcaaa6faaf83964
msgid "请问ESP-12F可以通过AT指令来控制模组的IO引脚的电平么？"
msgstr "Can ESP-12F control the level of module IO pins through AT commands?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:520 86a21f5df1c74c2789d494d2f5d3035d
msgid "通用固件不支持，需联系商务要支持IO控制的固件"
msgstr "The general firmware does not support this. Please contact sales for firmware that supports IO control."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:524 611ed189fe6342739b726d45fd344aa5
msgid "ESP-01S模组的蓝灯频繁闪表示什么？"
msgstr "What does frequent blinking of the blue LED on ESP-01S indicate?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:525 1a85cf909d074e828dbb586a98c4d275
msgid "表示模组工作中，蓝灯是log口"
msgstr "It indicates that the module is working. The blue LED is connected to the log port."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:529 4b557b68ebf14cbbbec7b811be0cd8c5
msgid "ESP-12F模组上的LED能点亮吗"
msgstr "Can the LED on the ESP-12F module be turned on?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:530 25f742ee482747e4aa7074323f2698b5
msgid "LED灯可以点亮，只需要把GPIO2引脚设置为低电平即可"
msgstr "Yes. The LED can be turned on by setting GPIO2 to low level."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:533 1d4ee985a04f4ce3aeebedc8b454d69a
msgid "请问ESP-01S模组的EN引脚是否需要接？"
msgstr "Does the EN pin of ESP-01S need to be connected?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:534 15a41bf4193041f294d1f12ca8f0ba60
msgid "需要外接一个上拉电阻。"
msgstr "Yes. An external pull-up resistor is required."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:537 82d2ac15ccb74a559112124cae2a1183
msgid "请问两个8266模块支持互相透传么？"
msgstr "Do two ESP8266 modules support transparent transmission with each other?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:538 fd81f6375750491aa0b3e1a872e4579e
msgid "作为服务器不支持透传功能，仅可单向透传；"
msgstr "As a server, transparent transmission is not supported. Only one-way transparent transmission is supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:541 ef25accfdea940709d1b60d269f2fbba
msgid "ESP-01S的规格书上的电压N表示什么意思"
msgstr "What does \"N\" mean for voltage in the ESP-01S datasheet?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:542 a592c62b158f4da8a567a7bff1c72bfa
msgid "N表示N/A 没有的意思，具体描述可以查看芯片手册"
msgstr "\"N\" means N/A, meaning not available. For details, refer to the chip manual."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:545 c19fed67a5114ee19fad65f38f06309d
msgid "ESP8266的那个RST脚链接的IO口有什么要求吗"
msgstr "Are there any requirements for connecting the RST pin of ESP8266 to an IO pin?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:546 48d6011ce9704b03ba8123aecab57b56
msgid "没有特殊的要求，低电平就是给模组硬件复位"
msgstr "There are no special requirements. A low level resets the module hardware."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:549 d23f09fca542437588352fb07a02d13f
msgid "请问一下ESP-01S模组的复位pin引脚是否需要接？"
msgstr "Does the reset pin of the ESP-01S module need to be connected?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/peripherals.rst:550 b98279ea36f04add847c1f39e4326583
